org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM spree_products INNER JOIN spree_product_properties ON spree_product_properties.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id WHERE spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_properties.name = "$1" AND spree_product_properties.value = 'Nike' AND spree_products.id = "$2" LIMIT 1
